# SR Linux partial startup-config, applied by containerlab after the node
# boots with its factory defaults. It sets the built-in admin user's
# password to `admin` so scripts/deploy_configs.py (SRL_PASSWORD=admin)
# can log in and push the compiled config. `admin` is a reserved username,
# so the password lives under `admin-user`, not `user admin`.
set / system aaa authentication admin-user password admin
